&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Directly manage and nurture a named account list and develop account plans for winning and expanding business with upper middle market and enterprise companies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
