&lt;p&gt;As a key member to the Stripe Platforms team, you will navigate complex organizations and ecosystems and identify ways Stripe can exceed expectations. We’re building something new, developing our sales process, our value proposition and assisting in the creation of key tools and assets. We’re looking for pioneers to join us on this adventure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
