&lt;p&gt;This Account Executive will drive sales and GTM strategy for the Financial Connections and Instant Bank Payments business. This role will involve collaborating closely with the product team to refine the GTM strategy, negotiate and close deals, and input into the roadmap to ensure that we’re constantly improving our product and growing the Link Network.&lt;/p&gt;
