&lt;p&gt;Our Global Sales team is hiring a Link Product Specialist Account Executive. Payments are at the core of Stripe’s business. In a global business environment, payments are complex and require deep enterprise knowledge to drive strategic conversations with our users. This Account Executive will drive conversion and cost optimization sales conversations covering Link, including Instant Bank Payments and Financial Connections.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Stripe, we&#39;re looking for people with passion, grit, and integrity. You&#39;re encouraged to apply even if your experience doesn&#39;t precisely match the job description. Your skills and passion will stand out—and set you apart—especially if your career has taken some extraordinary twists and turns. At Stripe, we welcome diverse perspectives and people who think rigorously and aren&#39;t afraid to challenge assumptions. Join us.&lt;/p&gt;
