&lt;p&gt;The team is segmented into two subteams: (1) The SMB AE team, which focuses on maximizing near-term revenue for Stripe through the acquisition of proven small and medium sized businesses that are unfunded, and (2) the Funded Startup AE team, which aspires to drive long-term revenue through the acquisition of early stage, high-potential, venture backed companies.&lt;/p&gt;
