&lt;li&gt;Identify, recommend and implement scalable accounting processes and automation improvements to support global growth in Bridge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with our business and finance partners to thoroughly understand new products, features, and contracts, and advise on accounting implications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research, prepare, and review technical accounting analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Internal Systems and Engineering teams to support internal financial systems and automation of accounting processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess the effectiveness of internal controls, and design new processes and controls for emerging and growing business activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain up-to-date accounting policies and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand data and system flows and related implications to accounting, with an aptitude to analyze financial results, and identify and problem solve financial anomalies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
