&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Backend Engineers at Stripe are comfortable working on new products under fluid conditions, seamlessly balancing tactical and strategic considerations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
