&lt;li&gt;A strong understanding of our business and products, and an ability to research/self-start&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience working with modern SaaS billing and invoicing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sophisticated business sense and understanding of underlying drivers and strategy of our user’s businesses&lt;/li&gt;
