&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a variety of Data Scientists to partner with the Product, Finance, Payments, Risk, Growth and Go-to-Market teams. You’ll work closely with a specific part of the business, playing a crucial role in optimizing our systems and leveraging data to make strategic business decisions. As Data Scientists as Stripe, it’s our mission to ensure that the company strategy, products, and user&amp;nbsp; interactions make smart use of our rich data, using&amp;nbsp; techniques like machine learning, statistical modeling, causal inference, optimization, experimentation, and all forms of analytics.&lt;/p&gt;
