&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Stripe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Stripe is a financial infrastructure platform for businesses. Millions of companies - from the world’s largest enterprises to the most ambitious startups - use Stripe to accept payments, grow their revenue, and accelerate new business opportunities. Our mission is to increase the GDP of the internet, and we have a staggering amount of work ahead. That means you have an unprecedented opportunity to put the global economy within everyone&#39;s reach while doing the most important work of your career.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Web Presence and Platform is organized into two pillars, each of which is grouped into pods that focus on the central tenets of Stripe&#39;s public mission. The Presence pillar creates industry-leading designs for Stripe’s front door surfaces, educates customers about the power of our platform, and drives our business success. The Platform pillar builds the internal machinery that powers these surfaces, and is responsible for making our websites fast, stable, and easy to modify.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Together we design and build stripe.com and other sites that amount to what is, for many, their first impression of Stripe. As such, WPP offers exciting opportunities to have a major impact on Stripe’s success. We want to make every pixel count, we want it to be enthralling, and we want to help other Stripes seamlessly benefit from our systematic work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Designer focused on Growth and SEO within the Web Presence and Platform (WPP) team, you will enhance Stripe’s organic search presence and user engagement through strategic design and content creation.&amp;nbsp;Your role will blend creative and analytical skills, managing multiple projects in a fast-paced environment to drive growth and engagement through innovative design solutions that captivate and convert users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Design and optimize organic landing pages for stripe.com to improve search visibility and user engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and develop interactive content tools (e.g., calculators, generators, templates) that provide utility to prospective businesses. Ensure the accuracy and reliability of these interactive tools, maintaining a high level of quality and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create visually engaging and user-friendly designs that align with Stripe’s brand standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product Marketing, Growth, and other cross-functional teams to understand user needs and behaviors, provide design solutions based on those insights, and to ensure the interactive content meets both business objectives and user needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on key performance indicators related to interactive content, providing insights to leadership on its impact on growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and refine design systems to optimize the website for SEO and growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct and analyze A/B and multivariate tests from a design perspective, implementing improvements based on findings, and analyze results to iterate and improve interactive content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and manage a growth process that drives key business metrics such as conversions, customer acquisition, and user engagement across our web presence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
