&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stripe Admin is an internal platform which is relied upon by Stripe employees globally for every part of their job: from talking with our users on the phone to launching a new feature and everything in between. Admin is an integral part of how we move quickly in service of our users.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
