&lt;p&gt;You’ll be part of the Japan Marketing team and be able to craft our enterprise marketing strategy while developing a strong trusted relationship working hand-in-hand with sales teams to drive successful user outcomes. The Enterprise Marketing Manager - Japan will set and execute a field marketing strategy and lead field marketing programs that deliver high-quality leads, sales pipeline, and ultimately revenue.&amp;nbsp; You will have an opportunity to shape the local Fin-tech market and elevate the local marketing team together with other marketing members at Stripe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft enterprise marketing strategy and execute field marketing programs across enterprise customer segments (established enterprises, digital native businesses, software platforms, ), with emphasis on the enterprise segment while solidly collaborating with Sales, SDRs, SAs and Professional services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own key business and revenue metrics across the sales funnel (pipeline) and customer growth and retention.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
