&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in pre-sales and sales of sizable service engagements, as well as in contract and Statement of Work (SOW) development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to lead large transformational engagements using disruptive technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrives on the urgency and importance of working with our largest customers, achieving set objectives while balancing competing priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
