&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stripe’s Global Sales Strategy and Operations team is responsible for the overall strategic direction of sales and supporting GTM teams. The team serves as a trusted advisor to the CRO and GTM Leadership team on the most impactful strategic issues, delivering high impact programs with multi-year trajectory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with the broader Sales Strategy &amp;amp; Operations team, the CRO and her leadership team, and key cross functional teams to drive near-term and longer-term global GTM strategy. This includes fiscal year GTM planning, identifying growth opportunities, leading strategic initiatives, and driving operational rigor and scale. You will be expected to leverage data to form recommendations and influence stakeholders to drive alignment and deliver results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor the progress, health, and sustainability of the overall strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide analytical rigor and strategic perspective to help inform key decisions across GTM teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand trends in business performance and derive insights on running the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a deep understanding of each area of the business to drive short-term improvement and long-term value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exhibit sound business judgment, strong collaboration and analytical skills, and a proven track record of taking ownership to influence results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to connect data driven insights with operational processes to drive efficiencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop point of view of resource, spend and program effectiveness, allocation strategy, and risks/opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain deep knowledge and understanding of Stripe’s business performance across geographies and user segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
