&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in sales strategy and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to break down problems of all different types in a structured fashion and identify the key issues to solve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to be “80/20” and understand and analyze key business signals and what they are telling us&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building models from scratch (in Excel or other planning applications)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience program managing complex cross-functional initiatives, ability to identify dependencies and unblock challenges&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to maintain high-performance under tight timelines, and an enthusiastic “roll up your sleeves” mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Excel, Salesforce (or similar CRM), data visualization tools (Tableau/PowerBI)&lt;/li&gt;
