&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced technology auditor with Fintech audit experience to help us deliver and expand a global audit program, who will serve as a key member of the IA technology audit pillar reporting to the Head of Technology Audit Pillar, and drive demonstrable business impact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
