&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have deep technical discussions with our engineering, operations and security teams to understand controls, processes deliver exceptional results through building and implementing audit programs that help protect our users and serve the business. Also, this person should be someone who has experience formally managing multiple audit and technical programs and enjoys them.&lt;/p&gt;
