&lt;li&gt;Plan and execute technical complex audits, consulting engagements, and other influencing activities of supporting operations, and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as IA’s SME on technology related considerations across IA audit projects and within the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage co-sourced service providers while delivering our audit plan.&lt;/li&gt;
