&lt;li&gt;Invest in understanding the business to better identify areas of need and opportunities to advise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and stay current on new technical literature applicable, emerging trends and best practices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
