&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Stripe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stripe is a financial infrastructure platform for businesses. Millions of companies—from the world’s largest enterprises to the most ambitious startups—use Stripe to accept payments, grow their revenue, and accelerate new business opportunities. Our mission is to increase the GDP of the internet, and we have a staggering amount of work ahead. That means you have an unprecedented opportunity to put the global economy within everyone’s reach while doing the most important work of your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’d be joining the Internal Communications team. Our team connects Stripe&#39;s global workforce with the company&#39;s strategic product vision and priorities by developing and executing impactful internal communications programs that build awareness, understanding, and engagement across the organization. We relentlessly uphold our &lt;a href=&quot;https://stripe.com/en-ca/jobs/culture&quot;&gt;operating principles&lt;/a&gt;, and we keep Stripe weird!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be responsible for developing and executing strategic communications programs that engage and inspire the Go to Market organization. You will support Stripe’s Chief Revenue Officer (CRO) by creating compelling content and facilitating impactful events that enhance our internal culture and values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Communications: Develop and execute strategic internal communications programs that connect, educate, and inspire Stripe’s revenue and sales organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Content Creation: Create clear and compelling written communications and produce engaging live events that support the CRO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stakeholder Collaboration: Partner with the CRO and the Go to Market leadership team to shape content and provide strategic counsel.&lt;/li&gt;
