&lt;li&gt;Experience with payments, risk, compliance, and/or financial services industry operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in Indian KYC regulations and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of building and managing high-performing teams&lt;/li&gt;
