&lt;p&gt;As a Launch Integration Engineer, you&#39;ll provide pooled technical consultation to users and Launch Managers, guiding them to successful Stripe implementations. We’re seeking candidates with technical and business skills to drive high quality integrations while accelerating the time to go-live process. You’ll work closely with cross-functional teams to drive product improvements, solve challenging and complex problems, and improve Stripe’s offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
