&lt;li&gt;Curious and enthusiastic about helping Frontier meet our goals, enjoy overcoming challenges, and react well under pressure or ambiguity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Low ego, with a proven track record of working well across teams and with external partners&lt;/li&gt;
