&lt;h3&gt;About the team&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Stripe Product Accounting Team is responsible for supporting all products at Stripe, consulting on accounting implications and supporting teams&#39; ability to make informed strategic decisions. We are responsible for the accurate and timely recording of all business-generated transactions on our balance sheet and income statement. We operate in a fast-paced environment and collaborate significantly with cross-functional and international teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
