&lt;p&gt;Stripe is seeking an Accounting leader to join its world class Accounting team and help us scale for the future, in a fast-paced environment that’s growing rapidly. We are responsible for all aspects of the financial, statutory, and internal reporting processes, financial systems, internal controls, and business support. In this role, you lead a team within Product accounting, leveraging your technical expertise to quickly identify accounting implications and impacts to customers while advising and collaborating with team members cross-functionally to develop operational processes that help us scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
