&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Research, prepare, and review technical accounting analyses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with Internal Systems and Engineering teams to support internal financial systems and automation of accounting processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
