&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain up-to-date accounting policies and procedures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understand data and system flows and related implications to accounting, with an aptitude to analyze financial results, and identify and problem solve financial anomalies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
