&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;10+ years of relevant public accounting and/or industry experience partnering with deal desk and sales functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;B.A. or B.S degree in Accounting or Finance (CPA strongly preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Fluency in U.S. GAAP and ability to research complex accounting issues&lt;/li&gt;
