&lt;p&gt;Our Design Systems team is responsible for design systems and user experiences across various products, including the Stripe Dashboard, internal tools, and external developer resources. You&#39;ll collaborate with other designers and managers on a broad range of design challenges, as we strive to create user-friendly experiences for our audience of product builders.&lt;/p&gt;
