&lt;li&gt;Prototype components and reusable end-to-end experiences, contribute to design system repositories, and support engineering efforts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain clear, comprehensive documentation to enable teams across the organization to adopt and extend the design system effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain shared UI libraries, patterns, and templates in Figma.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
