&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Have a passion for technology. &lt;/strong&gt;You are keen to learn about how things work and are able to explain technical concepts in ways that everyday people can understand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be Ambitious. &lt;/strong&gt;You are eager to make an impact at Stripe. You thrive in a fast-moving, dynamic, hyper-growth environment and are able to operate fluidly between the 30,000-foot strategy level and the micro-detail to get things right&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as a team player. &lt;/strong&gt;Product Marketers collaborate across the Marketing team and with basically every team at Stripe. You are able to work with a range of disciplines to execute on your work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
