&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive new business and revenue growth by selling &lt;strong&gt;Stripe Data Pipeline&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Sigma&lt;/strong&gt; to a variety of businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand and articulate the value propositions of both products to key stakeholders, including technical teams, financial departments, and C-suite executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of the data infrastructure, analytics, and reporting needs of potential customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relationships with clients, guiding them through the sales process and ensuring successful implementation of Stripe&#39;s data products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with the product, engineering, marketing, and customer success teams to ensure client satisfaction and long-term growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date on industry trends in data, analytics, and reporting to identify new opportunities and keep Stripe ahead of the curve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who meets the minimum requirements to be considered for the role. If you meet these requirements, you are encouraged to apply. The preferred qualifications are a bonus, not a requirement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of experience in a sales role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to understand technical products and communicate value to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of meeting or exceeding targets in sales or driving successful implementations of data products in a technical or analytical role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and presentation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated, with the ability to work in a fast-paced, results-driven environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the fintech, SaaS, or data analytics industries is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with data warehousing (e.g., Redshift, BigQuery, Snowflake) and ETL processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Past experience growing adoption of data and reporting software&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQL skills for querying and analyzing large datasets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in BI tools like Tableau, Looker, or Power BI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical certifications in cloud platforms or data tools (e.g., AWS, Google Cloud).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of financial data or payments infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Stripe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stripe is a financial infrastructure platform for businesses. Millions of companies - from the world’s largest enterprises to the most ambitious startups - use Stripe to accept payments, grow their revenue, and accelerate new business opportunities. Our mission is to increase the GDP of the internet, and we have a staggering amount of work ahead. That means you have an unprecedented opportunity to put the global economy within everyone&#39;s reach while doing the most important work of your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a member of the Link Product Strategy &amp;amp; Operations team you will be part of the Link Product organization, working directly with product management, engineering, and cross-functional teams to support the rapid growth of this new business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build thought leadership on the future state of Link and its overall strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tackle hard, ambiguous questions with rigor and independence, owning projects from problem definition to final recommendation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate white space business, product, and partnership opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead new or early stage initiatives or products, often playing the role of multiple functions simultaneously in order to reach success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape the product roadmap for the Link business, leveraging competitive and user insights to help PMs and Engineering teams prioritize.&lt;/li&gt;
