&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience at a growth stage Internet/software company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in the payments industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working as an SDR &amp;amp; AE.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of the APAC and EMEA region, specifically South East Asia, India, And markets across Europe.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
