&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Advanced proficiency in data analysis tools such as SQL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with risk management related concepts like card brand monitoring, compliance, or KYB/KYC requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
