&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a strong technical background, including 3+ years of experience with software engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy being a generalist working on both the frontend, backend, and anything it takes to solve problems and delight users both internally and externally&lt;/li&gt;
