&lt;li&gt;Experience building tools to improve developer productivity, and empathy for the end users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience writing high quality code in a major programming language, preferably golang, Ruby or Java.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
