&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of cloud platforms, micro-services, and event-driven architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of building scalable, high-availability systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent problem-solving skills and the ability to think strategically about risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience mentoring senior engineers&lt;/li&gt;
