&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in full time software development roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience as a technical leader in a software development role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can work effectively across the stack from top to bottom, comfortably navigating codebases with different languages and tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience as a technical lead, including defining the roadmap for complex projects spanning multiple teams and functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience mentoring and growing senior engineers as their technical leader&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You work very well cross-functionally and are comfortable making hard decisions and trade-offs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

