&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of software engineering, systems engineering and/or technical program management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical skills; you digest complex information and make recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a track record of providing program management during all phases of software development from kick-off to launch, demonstrating critical thinking, challenging the norms and thought leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have very strong written and verbal communication skills, building strong relationships with stakeholders, teams and senior leaders around the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
