&lt;p&gt;If this role isn&#39;t what you&#39;re looking for,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/jobs#open-positions&quot;&gt;please consider other open positions&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other Notes:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;*Please note this role is open to candidates outside of British Columbia. The information below is provided for candidates hired in those locations only.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The estimated pay ranges for this role are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based in British Columbia: CAD 97,700 - CAD 122,100&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
