&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;See yourself at Twilio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join the team as Twilio’s next International Tax Accountant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are &amp;amp; why we’re hiring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twilio powers real-time business communications and data solutions that help &lt;a href=&quot;https://customers.twilio.com/&quot;&gt;companies and developers worldwide&lt;/a&gt; build better applications and customer experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although we&#39;re headquartered in San Francisco, we have presence throughout South America, Europe, Asia and Australia. We&#39;re on a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;journey to becoming a global company that actively opposes racism and all forms of oppression and bias. At Twilio, we support &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/diversity&quot;&gt;diversity, equity &amp;amp; inclusion&lt;/a&gt; wherever we do business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is needed to work as part of a&amp;nbsp; global specialist International Tax Team.&amp;nbsp; You will spend your time collecting, analyzing, interpreting and reporting on information for tax purposes, assisting with the completion of tax returns and transfer pricing submissions for international entities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have the opportunity to use and develop your skills in a variety of tax applications, mainly related to financial reporting, compliance and tax optimisation work. You will add value through your ability to understand and communicate to others, including non-specialists, about tax matters and their impact on the business, and balancing conflicting demands and working to tight deadlines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work as part of the&amp;nbsp; International Tax team gathering, validating and compiling quantitative and qualitative tax information, from multiple internal and/or external sources, to ensure accuracy and completeness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carrying out financial and tax analysis and compiling reports for tax purposes including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Returns for Corporation Tax and Transfer Pricing filings&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax provisions for quarterly and annual US GAAP filings and Statutory Reporting and Accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Internal forecasts and tax reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax changes and their impact on the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicating and liaising with finance and business colleagues as necessary to check accuracy, give or obtain further information and/or resolve queries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring tax information and interpretation is presented clearly, unambiguously and in a readily comprehensible and appropriate format for the audience and business purpose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to robust tax processes, ensuring stringent financial control as well as compliance with Twilio policies and other regulatory requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to a wide variety of projects and initiatives to enable business objectives to be met in a tax efficient way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not all applicants will have skills that match a job description exactly. Twilio values diverse experiences in other industries, and we encourage everyone who meets the required qualifications to apply. While having “desired” qualifications make for a strong candidate, we encourage applicants with alternative experiences to also apply. If your career is just starting or hasn&#39;t followed a traditional path, don&#39;t let that stop you from considering Twilio. We are always looking for people who will bring something new to the table!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are someone who thrives in a fast- paced environment and can easily shift between the details and the “big picture”&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You love data and reconciliations with strong Excel and data analysis skills.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally, you have 1-3 years of experience working on International Tax matters within a multinational environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Third level qualification in Tax or Accounting, or relevant experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to influence and build effective working relationships with all levels of the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A desire to maintain and enhance our unique culture and an ongoing desire to strive for continuous improvement by adding your talents to Twilio is highly desired.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role can be based in Ireland, Canada or UK and is a remote role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are many benefits to working at Twilio, including, in addition to competitive pay, things like generous time-off, ample parental and wellness leave, healthcare, a retirement savings program, and much more. Offerings vary by location.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twilio thinks big. Do you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We like to solve problems, take initiative, pitch in when needed, and are always up for trying new things. That&#39;s why we seek out colleagues who embody our values — something we call &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/values&quot;&gt;Twilio Magic&lt;/a&gt;. Additionally, we empower employees to build &lt;a href=&quot;https://twilio.org/impact/2021-report/&quot;&gt;positive change in their communities&lt;/a&gt; by supporting their volunteering and donation efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
