&lt;p&gt;We like to solve problems, take initiative, pitch in when needed, and are always up for trying new things. That&#39;s why we seek out colleagues who embody our values — something we call&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/values&quot;&gt; Twilio Magic&lt;/a&gt;. Additionally, we empower employees to build&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.org/impact-fund/&quot;&gt; positive change in their communities&lt;/a&gt; by supporting their volunteering and donation efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
