&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is needed to maintain brand consistency across Twilio’s high touch, global virtual and in-person events. The Senior Graphic Designer&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Events&lt;/em&gt; role will align creative vision, consistently express brand nuance, and inspire event evolution across digital, print, product, video, and experiential mediums.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Brand team creates meaningful moments for current and future customers, showing the importance of human connection in a noisy digital world. Our dispersed, global team builds our brand through elevated content with engaging, high quality design. We set a creative and aspirational global standard for all Twilions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conceptualize creative design work&lt;/strong&gt; Lead visual concept development for large and small events in both physical and digital spaces. Execute your vision across a wide range of visual mediums including graphic design, illustration, video, and photography.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tell cohesive stories across mediums &lt;/strong&gt;to create immersive and delightful experiences that engage specific environments and audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate closely with creative peers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; including writers, lead designers, creative producers, or directors. Lead by example as a collaborator, taking direction to make a shared vision come to life.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cultivate cross-functional partnerships&lt;/strong&gt; through exceptional art direction of internal and remote teams, agencies, and talent, from creative, event teams, marketing, external booth vendors, developers, fabricators... etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Navigate concurrent Event projects&lt;/strong&gt; with aggressive timelines, without compromise. You learn on your feet and thrive in a dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovate through a mindset of creative problem-solving&lt;/strong&gt;. As plans change and new requirements arise, you’ll embrace the challenge with a fresh perspective.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not all applicants will have skills that match a job description exactly. Twilio values diverse experiences in other industries, and we encourage everyone who meets the required qualifications to apply. While having “desired” qualifications make for a strong candidate, we encourage applicants with alternative experiences to also apply. If your career is just starting or hasn&#39;t followed a traditional path, don&#39;t let that stop you from considering Twilio. We are always looking for people who will bring something new to the table!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developed creative design perspective&lt;/strong&gt; promoting high-level creative execution, graphic design fundamentals, brand cohesion, Accessibility, and human-centered design.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience building and working from creative briefs. &lt;/strong&gt;Comfortable taking the lead on projects, writing and shaping creative briefs, leading concept and ideation, timeline management and creative execution. Confident working with stakeholders, providing multiple viable solutions, articulating tradeoffs, and leading design direction.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exceptional writing and communication skills. &lt;/strong&gt;This role relies on articulating concepts with skill, navigating constructive critique, and facilitating others to do their best work. You can transform abstract and artful, into tactical and actionable. You have the ability and willingness to converse, explain, and engage in a dialog about creative ideas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In-house/agency brand team or extensive brand building experience. &lt;/strong&gt;Delighted by conversations exploring the facets of being ‘on Brand’. Experienced in brand infrastructure and expression across mediums and platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demonstrated experience partnering and art directing&lt;/strong&gt; remote teams, agencies, and talent. Understands the value of collaboration and creative partnership for building remarkable moments. Invites curiosity into creative dialogue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Large-scale event experience including digital and hybrid events.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A multi-faceted creative communicator: &lt;/strong&gt;as comfortable with physical exhibition design vocabularies, as they are with digital environments. Can work from print to screen, banners to icons, words to t-shirts. Inspired by the creative challenge of telling a story in never-before-seen ways.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong proficiency in creative working tools&lt;/strong&gt;: Adobe Creative Suite, Figma, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in physical or environmental design field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CAD, SketchUp, or 3D software is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will be remote and based in Colombia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Approximately 30% travel is anticipated.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are many benefits to working at Twilio, including, in addition to competitive pay, things like generous time-off, ample parental and wellness leave, healthcare, a retirement savings program, and much more. Offerings vary by location.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twilio thinks big. Do you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We like to solve problems, take initiative, pitch in when needed, and are always up for trying new things. That&#39;s why we seek out colleagues who embody our values — something we call&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/values&quot;&gt; Twilio Magic&lt;/a&gt;. Additionally, we empower employees to build&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.org/impact-fund/&quot;&gt; positive change in their communities&lt;/a&gt; by supporting their volunteering and donation efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, if you&#39;re ready to unleash your full potential, do your best work, and be the best version of yourself, apply now!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this role isn&#39;t what you&#39;re looking for, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/jobs#open-positions&quot;&gt;please consider other open positions&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twilio is proud to be an equal opportunity employer.&lt;/strong&gt; Twilio is proud to be an Equal Employment Opportunity and Affirmative Action employer. We do not discriminate based upon race, religion, color, national origin, sex (including pregnancy, childbirth, reproductive health decisions, or related medical conditions), sexual orientation, gender identity, gender expression, age, status as a protected veteran, status as an individual with a disability, genetic information, political views or activity, or other applicable legally protected characteristics. We also consider qualified applicants with criminal histories, consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. Qualified Applicants with arrest or conviction records will be considered for Employment in accordance with the Los Angeles County Fair Chance Ordinance for Employers and the California Fair Chance Act. Additionally, Twilio participates in the E-Verify program in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twilio is committed to providing reasonable accommodations for qualified individuals with disabilities and disabled veterans in our job application procedures. If you need assistance or an accommodation due to a disability, please contact us at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:accommodation@twilio.com&quot;&gt;accommodation@twilio.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;See yourself at Twilio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join the team as Twilio’s next Senior Manager - Analytics and Intelligence, Trust &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are &amp;amp; why we’re hiring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twilio powers real-time business communications and data solutions that help &lt;a href=&quot;https://customers.twilio.com/&quot;&gt;companies and developers worldwide&lt;/a&gt; build better applications and customer experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although we&#39;re headquartered in San Francisco, we have presence throughout South America, Europe, Asia and Australia. We&#39;re on a journey to becoming a global company that actively opposes racism and all forms of oppression and bias. At Twilio, we support&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.twilio.com/company/diversity&quot;&gt;diversity, equity &amp;amp; inclusion&lt;/a&gt; wherever we do business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is needed to lead a team of analysts that use data to ensure that all of Twilio’s communications are trusted and legal/compliant. This involves wide variety of activities including performing multiple analyses to effectively measure the volume of fraud in our communication channels along with building machine learning models that help detect fraud in near real-time .A successful candidate will be a self-starter, embody a growth mindset, collaborate effectively, can mentor junior analysts and operate as a thought leader in the Trust &amp;amp; Safety team. This role interfaces with several key stakeholders and works on initiatives that are tracked at the executive level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership and Strategy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the go to person for any data related questions from business stakeholders &amp;amp; executive leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Product &amp;amp; Engineering teams to understand overall trust &amp;amp; safety strategy &amp;amp; develop a vision and roadmap for the analytics team to help drive data enabled decisions, simultaneously use data &amp;amp; storytelling to help shape the broader strategy for the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and proactively monitor key fraud metrics to measure the volume of fraud across different product channels(Email, Voice &amp;amp; SMS) and provide thought leadership in helping identify product interventions that would mitigate emerging risks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a team of data analysts, scientists, and annotation specialists to develop data-driven solutions that enhance trust and safety across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and develop the analytics team inline with individual aspirations &amp;amp; business requirements,, provide guidance on technical skills, and career growth&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate second line of leadership within the team who can independently manage initiatives with stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytics Delivery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the development, implementation &amp;amp; maintenance of machine learning models that help detect fraud in real time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help build dashboards &amp;amp; develop metrics that provide a single source of truth to the entire trust &amp;amp; safety organization across multiple Twilio channels(SMS, Voice &amp;amp; Email)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build &amp;amp; maintain data pipelines to ingest data from multiple sources &amp;amp; vendors to enrich fraud measurement metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data to proactively identify gaps in our onboarding process &amp;amp; engineering systems being exploited by bad actors &amp;amp; help influence product roadmap &amp;amp; drive initiatives that reduce these gaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with stakeholders in trust and safety and other relevant orgs to understand their data and analytics needs, and deploy effective trust and safety measures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not all applicants will have skills that match a job description exactly. Twilio values diverse experiences in other industries, and we encourage everyone who meets the required qualifications to apply. While having “desired” qualifications make for a strong candidate, we encourage applicants with alternative experiences to also apply. If your career is just starting or hasn&#39;t followed a traditional path, don&#39;t let that stop you from considering Twilio. We are always looking for people who will bring something new to the table!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in analytics or data science roles with 5+ years of people management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience of working with stakeholders from various orgs(Product, Engineering &amp;amp; Operations) and navigating ambiguous problems at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent knowledge SQL and intermediate knowledge of data manipulation language such as R/Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience of building statistical models (e.g. classification/regression model, product experimentation, NLP use cases).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team player and comfortable interacting with people from multiple disciplines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing geographically distributed teams in a full remote environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience managing large teams of 10+ ICs, involving specialists in variety of roles - data analysts, data scientists &amp;amp; data engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in trust &amp;amp; safety domain, having performed investigative analyses of new threats and trends and usage of data to optimize rules and policies that defend against these threats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will be remotely based in India (Karnataka, Tamil Nadu, Telangana, Maharashtra, Delhi)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We prioritize connection and opportunities to build relationships with our customers and each other. For this role, you may be required to travel occasionally to participate in project or team in-person meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are many benefits to working at Twilio, including, in addition to competitive pay, things like generous time-off, ample parental and wellness leave, healthcare, a retirement savings program, and much more. Offerings vary by location.&lt;/p&gt;
