&lt;li&gt;Design and implement intern and new grad programs to provide meaningful and impactful experiences that are aligned with Twilio’s values and contribute to a diverse and inclusive workplace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver innovative strategies to attract top-tier talent and ensure Twilio remains competitive in the talent landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with internal stakeholders and leaders to understand hiring needs and align our strategies with business goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with universities, college and educational institutions in our key talent markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure effectiveness and health of our EIC strategies to make data informed decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
