&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build APIs, storage systems, cache layers and workflows to support complex business logic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other Engineers, Product Owners and Designers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in agile development with rapid, iterative, frequently deployed applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor other more junior engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
