&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of proven quota success in a sales/ISV sales role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of of India market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful track record of personally selling and closing solutions to software companies, telcos, system integrators or resellers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technically savvy and good understanding of SaaS solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success by achieving quota on a consistent and predictable basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience identifying, mapping and prospecting key prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to drive the sales process from internal leads to qualifying new prospects and handling deals to closure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent presentation and negotiation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal and communication skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build strong relationships with decision makers and C-level Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Bachelor’s degree or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Telco/CPaaS experience is highly desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience selling SaaS/CPaaS/Telco solution selling to a technical and business audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An understanding of the cloud computing/communications business model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
